description: Wracked by grief over Shiela's suicide, Dracula recalls past occurrences where he was similarly bereft. Blade the Vampire Hunter guest-stars!
name: Memories on a Mourning`s Night!

description: Dracula begins his takedown of the British Parliament…by killing a parliamentarian's daughter! Taj Nitall faces a tough choice – kill his own son or sacrifice his village.
name: Ten Lords a Dying!

description: Quincy Harker attempts to track Dracula's next move. Designer Daphne von Wilkinson has a run-in with a seriously depleted Dracula, giving her the upper hand in her quest for revenge.
name: Showdown of Blood!

description:
A collection of the adult work of Richard Moore as seen from Radio Comix and Anthill Comics, including the luscious furry adventures of The Pound, the romps in the forest of M’Lady, Tin God, imps and angels, and many delicious pin-ups of all species! Moore’s art is lush, gorgeous, raunchy, irresistible and...ahem...energetic. Warning: may become addictive.

Erotic comic, contains the following tails :

  • Fire and Brimstone
  • Tin God
  • M` Lady Don`t tease
  • M` Lady Magically Delicious
  • The Return of Frankenstein
name: Fire and Brimstone
